SUMMARY:Blood Drive
DTSTAMP:20260701T015051Z
DTSTART:20260711T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Houston Arboretum is partnering with the Gulf Coast Regiona
	l Blood Center to host regular blood drives at the Arboretum. Click a date
	 below to sign up to donate blood. All types of blood are needed to suppor
	t the needs of our city. All successful donors will receive a voucher for 
	a free Arboretum Individual Membership!  \n\n\n\n2026\n\n\n\n\n\n\njanuary
	 3\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nfebruary 7\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nMarch 7\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\
	n\n\nApril 4\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nmay 2\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\njune 13\n\n\n\n\n
	\n\n\njuly 11\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\naugust 1\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nseptember 26\
	n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\noctober 3\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nnovember 7\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
	\n\ndecember 12\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nIf all time slots are grayed out\, th
	ere are no more appointments available for that day. \n\n\n\nIf you are co
	ming to donate\, please use the 610 Entrance for easiest access to the Don
	or Coach. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQuestions?\n\n\n\nDonor AdvocatesDo you have que
	stions about your eligibility to give blood? Need more information about a
	 test result? Please contact us with any medical questions you may have be
	fore\, during or after your donation.  \n\n\n\nDonor Advocates team is ava
	ilable:  \n\n\n\n8 a.m. to 4 p.m. Monday–Friday  Email: donoradvocacy@give
	blood.org | Call: (713) 791-6608 The Blood Center will respond to your ema
	il within 24 hours during regular business hours. You may also check the E
	ligibility Page for basic eligibility questions: https://www.giveblood.org
	/donate/check-eligibility/ \n\n\n\nCustomer ExperienceDo you need to chang
	e your appointment? Have a question about our Donor Rewards program? Can’t
	 find your Donor ID? \n\n\n\nCustomer Experience team is available:  \n\n\
